  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ResourceToModelAdapter
    Adapts a Resource to it's ResourceModel using the ModelRegistry to lookup and the ResourceToModelMapper to map the model.
    ResourceToModelAdapterUpdater
    An AdapterFactory provides the type(s) it adapts from and the types it can adapt to as OSGi service properties.

Package io.neba.core.resourcemodels.adaptation Description

Contains generic adapter factories for adapting a resource to resource models, i.e. classes annotated with ResourceModel.
